column3: “I'm from Brooklyn ny and it's dope to get a strain like this. I was very surprised how strong of an indica hybrid it is, for me personally it puts me to sleep and I like that because I sometimes have trouble sleeping. I get a great fruity berry almost diesel like smell, buds are very dense. It may not seem icy but once you split it open it's a winter wonderland. You honestly could just take a few pulls or tokes and i...”
“best name ever. beautiful high. my head feels like butterflies.”
“Has a fruity smell especially when you split it open and see them crystal. Very heavy smoke..great for sleep”
“Very good strain made all my days worries melt away”
“I tried this last night.  I took 2 small hits, and soon after I was extremely dizzy.  Very powerful.  I didn’t care for it.”
“tried this and loved it! Also people here are so great!”
“Slight headache but really great and uplifting high”
